Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.82,0:00:12.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.23,0:00:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎你们回来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.09,0:00:16.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅行玩得开心吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.29,0:00:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.14,0:00:20.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早苗小姐 下次要跟我约会哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.98,0:00:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.74,0:00:24.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为 我们不是约定了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.52,0:00:27.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亏我还那么期待着跟早苗小姐的旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.04,0:00:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙 少泡别人老婆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.59,0:00:31.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿秋
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.22,0:00:35.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然 约会时汐也一起去 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.37,0:00:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也让我参加吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.20,0:00:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就我们三个人去开开心心玩吧 朋也 汐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.80,0:00:43.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别排挤我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.53,0:01:12.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.54,0:01:15.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋也
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.84,0:01:20.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都没变吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.29,0:01:24.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里我一直维持着她跟你结婚时的模样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.25,0:01:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 没变啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.22,0:01:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个你要拿走吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.06,0:01:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个布偶 汐也非常喜欢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.11,0:01:41.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长久以来非常之抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.79,0:01:42.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.73,0:01:44.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直将汐推给你们照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.31,0:01:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我察觉到身为父亲的职责
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.62,0:01:51.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果也是你开导的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.02,0:01:54.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并没有做什么事情哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.96,0:01:57.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她真的被养育得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.42,0:01:59.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不知该怎么道谢才好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.95,0:02:02.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 接下来我模仿一下江川
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.95,0:02:02.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs25}注：江川卓 原巨人队投手 退休后成为棒球解说者
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.47,0:02:04.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,江川～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.55,0:02:08.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 今后我想用自己的双手来养育她
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.11,0:02:13.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让她成长为像渚那样体贴而又坚强的人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.28,0:02:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时秋生和我为了渚而换了工作
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.57,0:02:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是在渚五岁时的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.77,0:02:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.31,0:02:26.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会用我的一生报答你们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.62,0:02:30.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 就请你变得幸福吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.45,0:02:35.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会幸福的 和汐一起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.58,0:02:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.57,0:02:39.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.39,0:02:44.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 汐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.13,0:02:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿秋说一起去打棒球吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.37,0:02:50.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.65,0:02:52.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.80,0:02:57.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然看到双眼像死鱼一样的家伙复活了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.90,0:02:59.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说啥废话 快投吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.71,0:03:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐 好好看清楚你老爸的狼狈相吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.22,0:03:05.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.38,0:03:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐觉得谁会赢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.72,0:03:08.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿秋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.88,0:03:09.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.67,0:03:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她可是看着我的豪腕长大的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.78,0:03:14.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.86,0:03:16.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我来把你的臭腕打烂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.88,0:03:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 可笑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.11,0:03:28.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.75,0:03:29.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了吗？汐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.03,0:03:31.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.09,0:03:35.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又得去道歉才行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.17,0:05:22.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&HDCFCD2&\3c&H89B87E&\4c&H6F9149&\shad1\bord1\pos(432,320)\fad(450,0)}家路
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.74,0:05:37.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早苗 你也没资格说别人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.38,0:05:40.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么从那天起就没哭过
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.45,0:05:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真清楚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.19,0:05:48.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了 你以为我是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.66,0:05:52.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我有了要做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.88,0:05:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必须养育汐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.15,0:06:01.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以很庆幸我并没有迷失自我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.41,0:06:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五年吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.11,0:06:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏汐我们也能有机会补偿什么了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.23,0:06:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 真的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.91,0:06:12.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过那也结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.29,0:06:14.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.04,0:06:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长久以来辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.68,0:06:22.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我们还是一家人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.74,0:06:27.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经 可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.57,0:06:30.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.52,0:06:33.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在轮到你哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.90,0:06:35.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.53,0:06:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算无可奈何我也会帮你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.67,0:06:41.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到你哭完为止我都会陪在你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.75,0:06:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 已经可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.18,0:07:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我们告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.44,0:07:17.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.72,0:07:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.92,0:07:20.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧 去狠狠地咬一口吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.28,0:07:23.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明白这意思吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.54,0:07:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天起就要跟爸爸两个人生活了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.57,0:07:28.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要乖哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.46,0:07:35.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后我工作忙时也要麻烦你们接送她到幼稚园
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.26,0:07:37.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心交给我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.86,0:07:40.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋也 关于那边的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.10,0:07:46.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白 近期我会去见个面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.47,0:07:53.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们已经从古河太太那里了解了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.08,0:07:56.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后请多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.60,0:07:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该我说才是 请您多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.45,0:08:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 汐 爸爸要去上班了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.70,0:08:05.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 路上小心 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.97,0:08:07.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.47,0:08:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 那个人就是那个冈崎先生了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.23,0:08:19.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直以来都干什么去了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.38,0:08:22.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟古河太太家之间有什么事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.38,0:08:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家庭争议？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.66,0:08:26.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前的我可能就已经发飙了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.94,0:08:28.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们好 我是冈崎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.31,0:08:31.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冈崎汐的父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.71,0:08:32.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.77,0:08:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.81,0:08:34.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为一些缘故
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.10,0:08:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直将女儿交给妻子的娘家照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.69,0:08:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但从今天起我开始和她一起生活了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.61,0:08:43.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你们多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.79,0:08:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 你多礼了 我们才是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.49,0:08:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家孩子也跟小汐很要好的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.42,0:08:52.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.29,0:08:56.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 开始一起生活了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.43,0:08:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 长久以来让你操心了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.02,0:09:03.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是很辛苦吧 一个大男人照顾一个小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.95,0:09:08.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最重要的时期 早苗小姐和大叔都帮我照顾过她了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.07,0:09:10.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算今后再怎么辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.27,0:09:13.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟他们相比根本不值一提
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.31,0:09:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有难处就随时跟我说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.79,0:09:20.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公司方面也会尽可能帮你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.44,0:09:22.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么现在我有个请求
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.81,0:09:26.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.86,0:09:28.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐 我来接你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.59,0:09:31.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.66,0:09:34.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然现在是夏季保育期间
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.45,0:09:37.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小汐的班主任请假了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.80,0:09:39.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请假…是生病了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.96,0:09:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是去了保育员的进修会
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.02,0:09:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下周会回来 所以到时再来谈谈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.91,0:09:48.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.78,0:09:52.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的老师是怎样的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.57,0:09:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长头发又漂亮又温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.56,0:10:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么爸爸要回去工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.67,0:10:04.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别人来了也不能开门哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.31,0:10:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事就打电话给早苗小姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.26,0:10:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道怎么打电话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.66,0:10:12.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.07,0:10:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天黑前我会回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.96,0:10:17.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.89,0:10:19.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.22,0:10:47.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.24,0:10:50.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是爸爸 双手都拿着东西了 帮我开下门吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.26,0:10:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从古河家拿来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.73,0:11:02.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,团子大家族和你的衣服还有玩具
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.58,0:11:05.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先摆放好这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.31,0:11:07.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放在哪里好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.68,0:11:13.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.02,0:11:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 就那里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.03,0:11:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸你会做菜吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.53,0:11:30.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后我会渐渐去学的 两个人一起学吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.50,0:11:33.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冈崎先生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.12,0:11:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.87,0:11:39.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久违了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.08,0:11:41.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多年不见了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.50,0:11:43.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就是？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.92,0:11:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我女儿汐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.70,0:11:47.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐 打个招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.92,0:11:49.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.60,0:11:53.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 你好 我是芳野公子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.29,0:11:59.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就是小渚的… 长得真像她呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.16,0:12:06.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想必会成为像小渚那样坚强又可爱的女性吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.23,0:12:09.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但愿如此呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.99,0:12:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她以前是妈妈的老师哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.61,0:12:16.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 我听芳野先生说了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.52,0:12:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你妹妹似乎出院了 恭喜你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.59,0:12:24.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 虽然医生说是个奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.70,0:12:26.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我们一直都相信她会醒来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.51,0:12:30.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实今天妹妹也一起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.04,0:12:33.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小风
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.44,0:12:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打招呼啊 他是姐姐的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.12,0:12:49.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就是你妹妹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.99,0:13:01.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你妹妹真有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.26,0:13:06.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小风 放心吧 他是姐姐的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.59,0:13:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是我妹妹风子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.76,0:13:12.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们是冈崎先生和小汐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.59,0:13:13.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次见面 幸会
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.86,0:13:15.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次见面 幸会
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.83,0:13:17.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次见面 幸会
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.99,0:13:21.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.78,0:13:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱 可以抱她吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.83,0:13:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么刚问完就抱了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.94,0:13:30.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小风 不能这样 很失礼的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.36,0:13:34.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 她就是这样子的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.97,0:13:36.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问她几岁了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.67,0:13:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你同年
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.23,0:13:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过一直睡着 本人感觉依然是高一时
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.00,0:13:49.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么我看下来跟汐没什么分别
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.85,0:13:53.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐和冈崎都好失礼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.53,0:13:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我生气了 所以她就做我的妹妹了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.29,0:13:59.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说这种莫名其妙的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.87,0:14:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁乱说也不行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.18,0:14:02.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.00,0:14:05.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常之可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.52,0:14:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有点怪 不过能交到新朋友真是太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.52,0:14:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐 爸爸明天也请了假
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.54,0:14:20.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你再陪陪我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.86,0:14:21.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又去旅行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.88,0:14:24.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是去旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.27,0:14:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也喜欢团子大家族吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.73,0:14:36.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早苗说过 这就是妈妈的气味
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.21,0:14:37.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.65,0:14:39.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好香
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.07,0:15:00.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.10,0:15:20.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 朋也君
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.76,0:15:32.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.40,0:15:34.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.15,0:15:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你憔悴了 老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.89,0:15:38.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.88,0:15:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是你的孙女
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.90,0:15:44.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.25,0:15:46.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.36,0:15:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.40,0:15:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直待在家里吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.32,0:15:55.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.90,0:15:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去见过你母亲了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.47,0:16:01.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.12,0:16:03.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和她去旅行的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.15,0:16:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在很远的北方 你以前带我去的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.77,0:16:10.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.83,0:16:13.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听她说了很多事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.76,0:16:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得你很辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.68,0:16:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想起了很多事 过去的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.32,0:16:26.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.62,0:16:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也累了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.02,0:16:29.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.61,0:16:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也应该可以…休息了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.87,0:16:38.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回乡下如何 你妈妈在等你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.57,0:16:43.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在你牵着我的手 发誓要亲手养育我的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.86,0:16:47.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.83,0:16:51.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经很努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.05,0:16:54.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 你就休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.88,0:16:58.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回乡下 和母亲一起生活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.03,0:16:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.82,0:17:20.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经…可以了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.01,0:17:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.46,0:17:25.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经完成职责了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.63,0:17:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是牺牲了一切 然后如此养育了我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.04,0:17:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了我这种不肖子 耗尽了自己的一生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.56,0:17:52.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经足够了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.30,0:18:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 不知不觉间就完成了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.98,0:18:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.26,0:18:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.56,0:18:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里有换洗用的衣服还有一点小钱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.93,0:18:41.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.17,0:18:47.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会联络那边的 别中途遗失行李了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.63,0:18:49.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我会小心注意的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.94,0:18:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家里的事我会处理好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.70,0:18:55.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,债款我也会解决的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.60,0:18:57.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.46,0:19:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐 来 跟爷爷说拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.59,0:19:03.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜 爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.27,0:19:13.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 就此告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.82,0:19:15.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意身体
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.03,0:19:16.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.79,0:19:20.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酒别喝太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.26,0:19:22.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.76,0:19:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋也 来 吃点心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.28,0:19:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也别抽那么多烟了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.68,0:19:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.05,0:19:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸又要出门了 别吃太多了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.56,0:19:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要活得长命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.46,0:19:39.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总让你孤零零一个 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.96,0:19:42.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝对会报答你的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.76,0:19:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来我一定会做晚饭给你吃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.17,0:19:47.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对会的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.31,0:19:49.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们两个人一起吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.99,0:19:56.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吗？朋也
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.96,0:20:06.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 朋也
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.47,0:20:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.17,0:20:23.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 汐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.89,0:20:26.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用为我担心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.88,0:20:30.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.16,0:20:33.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直以来 谢谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.20,0:20:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.17,0:20:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.94,0:20:44.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 保重
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.67,0:20:46.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋也 保重了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.54,0:21:00.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人过得幸福吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.22,0:21:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在最为幸福的时候 失去了心爱的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.46,0:21:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此后 和我两个人相依为命
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.49,0:21:12.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了我这种不孝子一路拼搏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.29,0:21:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样还算幸福吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.98,0:21:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.39,0:21:51.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 汐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.20,0:21:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.53,0:21:55.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得刺眼吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.09,0:21:56.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.76,0:23:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 汐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.04,0:23:45.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天有客人来找你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.77,0:23:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐 你会玩什么游戏吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.77,0:23:51.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐 跟妈妈说我出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.00,0:23:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 汐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.19,0:23:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很危险的 等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.24,0:24:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 加油
